    whyItMatters: 'Docker revolutionized software deployment by making environments reproducible, scalable, and portable. It eliminated the matrix of incompatibilities between development, staging, and production. Combined with orchestration platforms like Kubernetes, Docker enables microservices architectures where applications are decomposed into independently deployable services.',
